<lb ed="GA" n="0208a06"/>　旭山和尚　濟南和尚　明光和尚　成茂和尚　所清和尚　<note n="0208a0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，己【志彙】</note><app n="0208a0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">己</rdg></app>上各助英洋貳元</p></item></list>
<lb ed="GA" n="0208a07"/><p xml:id="pGA088p0208a0701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">光緒拾九年桂月天台山真覺寺敏曦募刻</p></cb:div>
